metadata.description: Airdropped items can be unlocked on https://companion-ape.com. Bored Ape Companion Club is a collection of 2,000 unique Companion Ape NFTs. BACC was airdropped as an event with the total trading volume of BAYC reaching 999,999 ETH on opensea. Airdropped items are locked and can be traded after unlocking.
